{"tid":614296,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵版 #MMA，拳拳到肉喎，點解冇人制止？","createTime":"2018-04-02T11:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T16:41:43.000Z","uid":174649,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcbe4648943284b354bd53d7db9e5befdc394e8","tid":614296,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"港鐵調景嶺站昨晚（4月1日）上演打鬥事件，兩男子疑因入閘時爭位發生爭執，繼至動武拳來腳往，乘客見狀報警，兩人雙雙受傷及被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨晚10時許，兩名分別49歲姓翁及29歲姓方男子，於港鐵調景嶺站入閘機前，疑因爭位發生碰撞，兩人初則口角繼至動武。有網民拍下事發經過，當時身穿白衣的姓方男子首先架起拳擊手勢及步法，雙手推開姓翁男子，翁男隨即放低背囊上前還擊，但被對方三度旋「掃堂腿」，途人經過見狀亦馬上走避。最後警方接報到場，將兩人涉嫌於公眾場所打架拘捕，姓翁男子腳及頭部受傷，姓方男子則面部擦傷及腹部紅腫，一同送往醫院治理。案件由將軍澳刑事調查隊調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1326557/org/237eac7b95b9d509e9a3dfa348530ba7.png/-AkK0Qulyry9w0zwmrStzBsx_p4GfxWhe9q8wHvavMA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1326557%2Forg%2F237eac7b95b9d509e9a3dfa348530ba7.png%2F-AkK0Qulyry9w0zwmrStzBsx_p4GfxWhe9q8wHvavMA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=facda99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1326559/org/c347fd0cba96dc8a7d0c271fb14e85f2.png/A9V8ea70b2kE5Ey7kOFoMv08gU6oA9LLSNSs2kjUrNo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1326559%2Forg%2Fc347fd0cba96dc8a7d0c271fb14e85f2.png%2FA9V8ea70b2kE5Ey7kOFoMv08gU6oA9LLSNSs2kjUrNo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=65d19260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1326563/org/0933a26dad94350d8373fb24db09d265.png/Qh2StCtaKFU_ByD1Re0N-R5kGrsCk5I3EIM5xxCDOcc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1326563%2Forg%2F0933a26dad94350d8373fb24db09d265.png%2FQh2StCtaKFU_ByD1Re0N-R5kGrsCk5I3EIM5xxCDOcc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c6541941&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e12a17b47187976c376694cf0946b0528f885727","tid":614296,"uid":174649,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0